1. Title of dataset: Climate Data obtained from DHM
2. Author information
	Published by:
		Department of Hydrology and Meterology
		Government of Nepal
		Ministry of Energy, Water Resources and Irrigation
	
3. Data of data collection (single date or date range): 2014, 2017, 2018 for weather summary, 1980-2010 as reference for climate normal.


