2. Number of cases / (from third columns): 21 stations

3. Missing data codes: None

4. Variable list
	Mean Temperature, Maximum Temperature, Mean Temperature, Precipitation
	
	Unit of measurement: 
		Precipitation : mm
		Temperature: Celsius

